attributes.review: Hello fellow Trump supporter here 🤩 #makeamericagreatagain. I decided to download this app because of my total complete and everlasting loyalty toward my one and only savior DJT. Anyways, worse mistake of my life 😳. After I downloaded and opened the app my father (fasa) was trampled by wildebeest 🤧. I ran toward him and screamed but it was too late 😩. My uncle (car) came into the room and told me it’s because I am a fellow person of color going against my own kind and supporting DJT 😐. I couldn’t believe it. He told me to leave! To go and never come back because then my family would have discovered what I did 🥴. SoI had to go on the run 😤. I left my family and friends even though I am the rightful heir to the throne and it is my right to become Queen and defend my home 😔. They probably think I’m dead honestly, but on the bright side I made some new friends named imon and umba. They found me past out after running for so long and took me to their home where apparently it’s normal to eat bugs 😳. I was starting to get used to it though, living life one day at time and all. But then I bumped into an old friend of named ala 🥰. She told me that my uncle had gone rouge and was holding my family hostage and she managed to escape😤. I went back home and fought my uncle to the death 💪. I won. But at a cost of sacrificing loved ones 😔. Do not download this app 😰 it will come at cost and you may not be able to fight whatever challenges may come your way 🤭. So I will no longer be voting for DJT😭. I’m so sorry my fellow white supremicists 🤗 may we live to fight another day !
